high_descs: Turn to the left, go to the fridge and hang a right, go to the counter on the right where the bowl is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn around, go forward, then turn to the right just before the stove.
Use the butter knife to cut the potato into slices.
Turn around, go forward to the counter, hang a left then turn to the right to the fridge.
Put the butter knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, go forward to the counter where the potato is.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn around, go forward then hang a right and go to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, rinse it off, then pick it back up.
Turn around, go forward, then hang a right and go to the fridge.
Put the potato inside the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and clean potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the corner of the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the left to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife on the middle shelf in the fridge.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn to the left and walk forward to face the sink.
Wash the slice of potato in the sink, and then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice on the top shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To clean a potato slice and place it on the top shelf in the fridge.
